<TITLE> Ex-bodyguard of 'Bangla Bhai' arrested </TITLE>
<TEXT>
 Bogra, Apr 17 (bdnews24.com)Former bodyguard of Siddiqur Rahman alias 'Bangla Bhai', military commander of banned Islamist outfit Jama'atul Mujahidin Bangladesh, was arrested Friday in Gabtali Upazila of the district, police said Friday. "'Russell', alias 'Gittu Russell' is a top-listed militant of the district," Gabtali Police Station officer-in-charge Tofazzal Hossain said. Police arrested the fugitive on a tip-off at his home at Karnibari in the Upazila at around 2pm. The spiritual chief, Shaikh Abdur Rahman, and Bangla Bhai were hanged in 2007. bdne
